Problem Statement¶

Predict the bankruptcy of the companies based on various markers and and financial ratios of various entities.

  • Target variable is whether the company got bankrupt in the subsequent years or not.
  • Using the data build appropriate model to ascertain the bankruptcy of entity.

Model Building¶

Function for printing evaluation metrics

In [107]:
def error_metrics(pred_test,y_test):
    confusion_df = pd.DataFrame({'actual':y_test,'predicted':pred_test})
    print("Confustion Matrix\n",pd.crosstab(confusion_df['actual'],confusion_df['predicted']),"\n")
    print("Accuracy:",accuracy_score(pred_test,y_test),"\n")
    print("Precision, Recall, F1-score\n",classification_report(y_pred=pred_test,y_true=y_test),"\n")

Define Custom funciton for recall

In [169]:
def recall(y_true,y_pred):
    TP = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true*y_pred,0,1)))
    AP = K.sum(K.round(K.clip(y_true,0,1)))
    recall = TP / (AP + K.epsilon())
    return recall
